_stream:{fwb.type=$type,fwb.subtype in (${sub_type:doublequote})}
| fwb.main_type:(${main_type:doublequote}) AND fwb.action:(${action:doublequote}) AND fwb.threat_level:(${threat_level:doublequote})
| $Logsql
| count() total_logs, count_uniq(fwb.subtype) unique_subtype, count_uniq(fwb.attack_type) unique_attack_type, count_uniq(fwb.main_type) unique_main_type, count_uniq(fwb.severity_level) severity_level

| $Logsql
| stats by (source.ip,fwb.action) count() results 
| sort by (results) desc 
| limit 10
